### 3. COMMERCIAL LICENSE (RESERVED — NOT CURRENTLY REQUIRED)

> The Software is free today (Section 2). This section describes a possible future paid tier and does not
> apply to current use — no purchase is required to use the Software now.

#### 3.1 Purchase & Activation
If a paid tier is introduced, a Commercial License would be sold on a per-seat, per-year basis at Licensor's standard rates. Upon purchase, you would receive a license key; activation is automatic upon entry of a valid key in the Software settings.

#### 3.2 License Tiers
Licensor offers the following license tiers (subject to change):
- **Solo**: Single user, single machine
- **Team**: 2–5 users, unlimited machines
- **Enterprise**: 6+ users, unlimited machines, priority support

If and when a paid tier launches, terms and pricing will be published at [experttags.com](https://experttags.com).

#### 3.3 Renewal
Any future Commercial License would be renewed annually, with renewal notices at least thirty (30) days before expiration. (Not applicable while the Software is free.)

