### 5. DATA & PRIVACY

#### 5.1 Local Storage
The Software processes and stores label designs, templates, and data files locally on your computer. Licensor does not access, collect, or transmit this data unless you explicitly authorize export to a machine or cloud service.

#### 5.2 No Telemetry
The Software contains no telemetry, analytics, or usage tracking features. You have full control over your data.

#### 5.3 Credentials
Machine credentials (API keys, auth tokens) are stored in your operating system's credential store (Windows DPAPI, macOS Keychain, Linux Secret Service) and are never transmitted to Licensor without your explicit request for support.

### 6. MACHINE ADAPTERS

The Software includes adapters for third-party machines (Trotec, Panduit, Roland, etc.). Use of these adapters is subject to the terms of service and licensing agreements of those vendors. Licensor is not responsible for third-party hardware failures, data loss, or licensing disputes with vendors.

